OL,3,CNoise complaints in Ambleside amid
OL,4,Congoing home constructions
OL,6,FITV Border reporter Fiona Marley-
OL,7,FPaterson went to Ambleside to meet
OL,8,Fthose affected
OL,10,FResidents in Ambleside have complained
OL,11,Fabout noise caused by the construction
OL,12,Fof homes in their area.
OL,14,FBuilding work has been ongoing since
OL,15,Fthe National Park approved plans to
OL,16,Fbuild forty homes near Loughrigg Park.
OL,17,FBuilders are now having to dig through
OL,18,Fthick rock, causing the noise.
