OL,3,CNoise complaints in Ambleside amid
OL,4,Congoing home constructions
OL,6,FResidents say it's been noisy for nine
OL,7,Fweeks, but the Council say that a lack
OL,8,Fof affordable housing in the region
OL,9,Fmakes the work necessary.
OL,11,F"We can't use our home; we can't use
OL,12,Four garden; we can't have windows and
OL,13,Fdoors open because the disruption is
OL,14,Fso awful," said one local resident,
OL,15,FGill Dixon.
