OL,3,CNoise complaints in Ambleside amid
OL,4,Congoing home constructions
OL,6,F"It just about drives you mad. We have
OL,7,Frespite for half an hour when the men
OL,8,Fare having their lunch. We just can't
OL,9,Fget away from it because it starts
OL,10,Fabout half eight in the morning, goes
OL,11,Fon to a quarter to five at night."
OL,13,F"It's this peck, peck, pecking all day
OL,14,Flong. It's the vibration, the knock,
OL,15,Fknock, knock all day."
OL,17,FHowever, there is a severe housing
OL,18,Fshortage in the Lake District, with
OL,19,Fsome blaming high tourist numbers and
OL,20,Fsecond homes for driving up prices.
