OL,3,CNoise complaints in Ambleside amid
OL,4,Congoing home constructions
OL,6,FGenna Graham has been living in a van
OL,7,Fbecause she can't find anywhere to
OL,8,Flive locally.
OL,10,F"I was actually born in Kendal. I have
OL,11,Fall my links here: my family, my
OL,12,Fschool and I've still been waiting a
OL,13,Fyear and a half on the council list
OL,14,Fand I've been placed in hotels and
OL,15,Fvarious different sort of emergency
OL,16,Faccommodation situations. It happens
OL,17,Fto anybody. They say we're only one
OL,18,Fpaycheck away from being homeless,
OL,19,Faren't we?
