OL,3,CNoise complaints in Ambleside amid
OL,4,Congoing home constructions
OL,6,F"I've still got a roof over my head.
OL,7,FThere's people living in tents.
OL,8,FThere's families living in tents. The
OL,9,Ftrouble with not having a stable
OL,10,Faddress is that I can't get stable
OL,11,Femployment. I'll be honest, when I got
OL,12,Fthe van, I was really pleased because
OL,13,FI could cook for the first time in
OL,14,Fwhat had been months. "
OL,16,FResponding tor requests for comment
OL,17,FThe National Park said the noise was a
OL,18,Fbreach and that the developer has made
OL,19,Fchanges.
