OL,6,FThe developer hasn't commented, but in
OL,7,Fa statement a spokesperson for
OL,8,FWestmorland and Furness Council, said:
OL,9,F"The lack of affordable housing is a
OL,10,Fnational issue but also a key priority
OL,11,Fwithin Westmorland and Furness
OL,12,FCouncil's Council Plan.
