OL,3,CNoise complaints in Ambleside amid
OL,4,Congoing home constructions
OL,6,F"Westmorland and Furness Council is
OL,7,Fcommitted to supporting more housing
OL,8,Fto meet all needs so that local
OL,9,Ffamilies can build a life here, new
OL,10,Fpeople can be attracted to relocate
OL,11,Fand older residents and those with
OL,12,Fdisabilities are able to live as
OL,13,Findependently as possible whilst
OL,14,Freceiving the support they need.
OL,16,F"We support high quality housing that
OL,17,Fis affordable, well designed and
OL,18,Fenergy efficient, and accompanied by
OL,19,Fappropriate infrastructure to support
OL,20,Fcommunities."
